{"tid":710395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聯署]Shadowverse香港玩家發起聯署,抗議日本「國際服」營運廠商強制轉移香港玩家數據至中國服","createTime":"2018-06-20T17:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T04:55:53.000Z","uid":40108,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b463a8f5427f5bba4376e7d4c8778699d4fd938e","tid":710395,"uid":40108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"訓之前追POST見到好似有進一步行動, 所以試下幫手整理, 略盡綿力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聯署: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfkx7pfF_ZbXG7vb4hzlBxiYV6rPfmg-vfywmKcmS1l-4b7cA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfkx7pfF_ZbXG7vb4hzlBxiYV6rPfmg-vfywmKcmS1l-4b7cA%2Fviewform&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=16562857\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfkx7pfF_ZbXG7vb4hzlBxiYV6rPfmg-vfywmKcmS1l-4b7cA/viewform</a><br />\n唔係SV玩家都可以簽, 揀唔係玩家就OK<br />\n之前如果填左嘅SV玩家唔洗再填<br />\nCygames旗下遊戲嘅玩家都可以填<br />\n但唔好重複或者亂填id（Cygames會check）<br />\n<br />\nQuote番上個POST D比較重要資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/705533/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/705533/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n事源官方公告:<br />\n<a href=\"https://shadowverse.com/cht/news/detail.php?announce_id=662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshadowverse.com%2Fcht%2Fnews%2Fdetail.php%3Fannounce_id%3D662&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=98e878b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://shadowverse.com/cht/news/detail.php?announce_id=662</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人包:<br />\n1. 2016年開左國際SER<br />\n2. 好多香港人一早已經玩緊<br />\n3. 2018年4月開左中國SER<br />\n4. 2018年6月14日突然公告話要將港澳玩家DATA轉去中國SER<br />\n而事前係無任何通知同協商, 而國際服係會BLOCK 埋香港澳門IP<br />\n即係逼你轉中國服, 唔轉無得玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/145002_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F145002_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5626be5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQuote番巴哈原文<br />\n其中一項係寫比官方嘅公開信<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\nI. 致官方的公開信<br />\n內文如下<br />\n中文: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/UE9nkG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FUE9nkG&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=f8589f17\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/UE9nkG</a><br />\n英文: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/Fb2gc1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFb2gc1&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=e59460e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Fb2gc1</a><br />\n日文: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/X1rbzq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FX1rbzq&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=3aa4b55a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/X1rbzq</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter公開信推文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ayame93945354/status/1008234922933227521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAyame93945354%2Fstatus%2F1008234922933227521&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=f9554727\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAyame93945354%2Fstatus%2F1008234922933227521&h=a464c43e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Ayame93945354/status/1008234922933227521</a><br />\n請各位轉推及LIKE，因為這兩項越多就意味越有機會得到關注。<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n巴哈原文有興趣就自己追<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29330&amp;snA=14113&amp;tnum=13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29330%26snA%3D14113%26tnum%3D13&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=3b3c6cef\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29330&amp;snA=14113&amp;tnum=13</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29330&amp;snA=14067&amp;tnum=14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29330%26snA%3D14067%26tnum%3D14&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=0595c9cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29330&amp;snA=14067&amp;tnum=14</a>"},{"pid":"9e91f1f29a058d6781a8dded16d5dbe3131f5501","tid":710395,"uid":40108,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:08:29.000Z","msg":"其中公開信有幾點值得關注<br />\n<br />\n三、按照國際慣例，大部分線上遊戲均會將香港納入亞洲區 或 與台灣、澳門區合併，甚至是把香港獨立於中國區而非納入中國區來處理。<br />\n<br />\n四、承接三，因此香港人及澳門人應享有選擇登錄國際服的自由。<br />\n<br />\n六、我們非常憂慮遊戲資訊及交易紀錄受到中國監控。<br />\n我們無法相信中國會保障我們的私隱權益，並擔心個人交易資料會被盜用。<br />\n<br />\n九、由於這次轉移事件是前所未見的先例，我們極為擔心此舉將會引起骨牌效應，導致未來會有更多日本營運公司仿傚，而把香港納入中國區處理。<br />\n甚至將來在遊戲業務以外、以及日本以外的國家公司，均會把香港納入中國區處理。這將會對香港人的自由與權利構成重大衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知簽完有冇用, 不過簽左先好過咩都無做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced117553781958724e1537cbfbb35b8f35e7833","tid":710395,"uid":40108,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ayame93945354/status/1009433260361859072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAyame93945354%2Fstatus%2F1009433260361859072&d=En0ltqR17WZl%2Bf5Y1kYour5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=ad15d3ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAyame93945354%2Fstatus%2F1009433260361859072&h=fdde41d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Ayame93945354/status/1009433260361859072</a><br />\n<br />\n好似上到去日本官方twitter做宣傳, 搵日本仔幫手簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫得咁多, good luck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW 宣傳圖又幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DgI6KCzWsAUfMwJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/